rows.label: qst201413_msg0001
rows.name: Hey. Still up?

rows.label: qst201413_msg0002
rows.name:
Yeah. We're trying to figure out which
of us has the most Girl Power. We're
comparing our girl talk skills.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0003
rows.name:
Mei, since you're here, will you be
our judge?

rows.label: qst201413_msg0004
rows.name: Sure. I'll be fair and frank.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0005
rows.name:
You look great even in the middle of
the night, Mei.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0006
rows.name:
Hmmm... The darkness matches my
soul, I suppose.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0007
rows.name:
After all, I am what they
call a nightstalker!

rows.label: qst201413_msg0008
rows.name: What are you talking about, Mei?

rows.label: qst201413_msg0009
rows.name: I said, I'm a nightstalker. Deal with it.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0010
rows.name:
Only the chosen ones can wield the
power of darkness. That's how you
know I'm a nightstalker.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0011
rows.name:
Only the Lightbearer can resist one
such as me.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0012
rows.name:
Light and dark are in a constant
struggle. A never-ending war, known
as the Sacred Contest.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0013
rows.name:
We conserve our power and stand
poised, each staring at the other with
the coiled power of a hungry tiger.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0014
rows.name:
But one dawn, the dark shall surely be
victorious.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0015
rows.name:
And a new world of nightstalker
domination will be reborn!

rows.label: qst201413_msg0016
rows.name:
Yes... I wait patiently for the dawn of
that black sun...

rows.label: qst201413_msg0017
rows.name:
Hikari... Do you know what she's
talking about?

rows.label: qst201413_msg0018
rows.name: Not a word of it.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0019
rows.name:
I've never heard of anything like it.
Not even 500 years ago.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0020
rows.name: Ah, Mei... She's certainly special.

rows.label: qst201413_msg0021
rows.name: She sure is.
